      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "COLFAX, Wash. Oct. \"A sensa-\nton is promised when the city coun-\nell takes up the request to revoke the\nlicense of a lessee of City Marshal\nWeinberg. The fight has been long\none on the part Of the temperance\npeople. Last Sunday the sheriff. it\nis said, obtained bottle of whisky\nIn the saloon, via the dumb waiter\nroute. which Is considered enough\nevidence of selling liquor on Sunday.\n\n\n1t is predicted that Weinberg will\nbe removed from office for allowing\nhis building to be used in an unlawful\nmanner. and the prosecuting attorney\nstands ready to file an information\nagainst the proprietor of the saloon\nin the superior court"
    }
  ]
